Interface NumericalAssignmentGroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AttributeAssignment, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NumericalAssignmentGroupImpl

    public interface NumericalAssignmentGroup
extends AttributeAssignment
    A representation of the model object 'Numerical Assignment Group'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Ingredient Concept
    • Substance
    • Numeric Value
